snippet.title: Spirit City: Lofi Sessions - First Look Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2113850/Spirit_City_Lofi_Sessions/

Welcome to the cozy world of Spirit City!
In Spirit City: Lofi Sessions, you may unwind, study, or work while surrounded by tranquil vibes, and use productivity tools to stay on task. Immerse yourself as you listen to lofi music, customize your avatar and explore the soothing soundscapes.

Discord : discord.gg/6dbezgFSkQ 
Instagram : https://instagram.com/spiritcitylofi
Twitter : https://twitter.com/SpiritCityLofi
Tiktiok : https://tiktok.com/@spiritcitylofi
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/wearemooncube

♪  Cozy Oni - Tranquil Whispers
